articles.title: KL Rahul, Ravindra Jadeja seal a tough chase in 1st Australia ODI - Hindustan Times
articles.description: India were in a spot of bother at 83/4 but the duo played some smart cricket to take the hosts to victory | Cricket
articles.content:
For the second time in 2023, KL Rahul walked out at no 5 with his side in trouble and he once again managed to bail India out in a tricky run-chase.
